00:53:46,803 --> 00:53:48,604
You get to a point where,

1106
00:53:48,605 --> 00:53:51,439
either that bill doesn't get
paid or your children don't eat;

1107
00:53:51,440 --> 00:53:53,844
so, obviously,
your children eat.

1108
00:53:55,844 --> 00:53:59,113
So, looking
at the world of cutbacks,

